eu.opends.hmi

Class PresentationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.opends.hmi.PresentationModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LocalDangerWarningPresentationModel, RedTrafficLightPresentationModel, RoadWorksInformationPresentationModel, TrafficLightPresentationModel

    public abstract class PresentationModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class used to compute the distance between the moving car and any target position. The target position is further described in its subclasses.
    Author:
    Rafael Math
